Dato' Wira Ir. Haji Amiruddin bin Hamzah (Jawi: اميرالدين بن حمزه) is a Malaysian politician. He is a member of the Malaysian United Indigenous Party (BERSATU) and member of parliament for Kubang Pasu. He was appointed Deputy Finance Minister of Malaysia in July 2018.Amiruddin was a Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party (PAS) member until he quits to join BERSATU in 2017.Amiruddin is married to Nora Mohamed Noor.


